  <title>Usage of the <command>grafana-container-manage.sh</command> script</title>
  <para>
    The <command>grafana-container-manage.sh</command> script is used to manage
    the &grafana; container on the &alp; (&alpshort;). This article lists each
    subcommand of the script and describes their purpose.
  </para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term><command>grafana-container-manage.sh create</command></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Pulls the &grafana; image and creates the corresponding container.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term><command>grafana-container-manage.sh install</command></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Installs additional files that are required to manage the &grafana;
          container.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term><command>grafana-container-manage.sh start</command></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Start the container called <literal>grafana</literal>.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term><command>grafana-container-manage.sh uninstall</command></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Uninstall all files on the host that were required to manage the
          <literal>grafana</literal> container.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term><command>grafana-container-manage.sh stop</command></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Stop the <literal>grafana</literal> container.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term><command>grafana-container-manage.sh rm</command></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Delete the <literal>grafana</literal> container.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term><command>grafana-container-manage.sh rmcache</command></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Remove the container image in cache.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term><command>grafana-container-manage.sh </command></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Runs the <literal>grafana</literal> container.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term><command>grafana-container-manage.sh bash</command></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Runs the <command>bash</command> shell inside the
          <literal>grafan</literal> container.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term><command>grafana-container-manage.sh logs</command></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Displays log messages of the <literal>grafan</literal> container.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
